      "date": "2012-09-25 01:25:20.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.8/x86_64, CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/171f317a-06ac-11e2-9b17-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
